Lois Winstone https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lois_Winstone 0 Lois Elaine Winstone (born 1982) is an English actress and musician. Her younger sister Jaime is also an actress. She has had parts in both Holby City and The Bill, as well as in several films. Lois_Elaine_Winstone ( born 1982 ) is an_English_actress_and_musician . Her_younger_sister_Jaime is also an_actress .
